name: Kyten Technologies
long_description:
Kyten Technologies builds custom, turnkey battery packs for air, sea, and space vehicles. 
100,000+ autonomous vehicles are coming to the air, sea, and space, but the legacy supply chain can't keep up. 
During our six years at Starlink, we put 5,000+ battery packs into space. Now, we're bringing rapid development and volume production of aerospace-grade battery packs to the entire industry.
one_liner: Custom, turnkey battery packs for aerospace vehicles
